<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">ش وق:</span> <span class="c2">(الشَّوْقُ)</span> وَ <span class="c2">(الِاشْتِيَاقُ)</span> نِزَاعُ النَّفْسِ إِلَى الشَّيْءِ،<span class="c5"> يُقَالُ:</span> <span class="c2">(شَاقَهُ)</span> الشَّيْءُ مِنْ بَابِ قَالَ فَهُوَ <span class="c2">(شَائِقٌ)</span> وَذَلِكَ <span class="c2">(مَشُوقٌ)</span> وَ <span class="c2">(شَوَّقَهُ فَتَشَوَّقَ)</span> أَيْ هَيَّجَ شَوْقَهُ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>